I signed up to Drooble months ago and I'm pretty satisfied by it. I'm not a musician, I'm just a music fan and I found lots of people who have the same taste in music as mine. Also, I found a singer for the music project of a friend of mine. Love reading Drooble's blog - at last a blog where they post interesting music-related articles in an understandable language. In other words - I strongly recommend Drooble for both music fans and musicians.
